Package: idf
Title: Extending the 'raster' package with reading and writing idf rasters
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kees",
           family = "van Immerzeel",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "idodoes@xs4all.nl")
Description: Extending the 'raster' package in order to be able to read and write idf rasters.
    IDF is a simple binary format used by the iMOD groundwater modelling software.
    The format contains a header with grid and spatial extent information and
    an array of floats.The array of floats is translated to a rectangular grid using
    the ncol and nrow fields of the header.
URL: https://oss.deltares.nl 
